    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 16 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 4 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 16</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>Make an unarmed attack against all adjacent creatures, which deals normal damage. Feats like Cleave or Great Cleave will not activate if you kill an enemy this way. You suffer a -4 penalty to Learn checks when learning this technique if you do not have the Gouken feat.</p>\n\n\n\n",
